        <div class="notes-content">
            <h3>Design System Reference</h3>
            <p>All components should follow the patterns documented in <code>DESIGN_SYSTEM.md</code>. Key principles:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Colors:</strong> Use only colors from the approved palette</li>
                <li><strong>Gradients:</strong> Apply gradients for emphasis and hierarchy</li>
                <li><strong>Animations:</strong> Use cubic-bezier easing: <code>cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1)</code></li>
                <li><strong>Typography:</strong> Space Grotesk font family exclusively</li>
                <li><strong>Border Radius:</strong> Use scale: 8px, 12px, 16px, 20px, or 24px</li>
                <li><strong>Spacing:</strong> Follow 8px grid system</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Creating New Components</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>Check if a similar component exists in this examples page</li>
                <li>Reference the design system for colors and patterns</li>
                <li>Apply glass morphism for overlays and panels</li>
                <li>Add neon glow effects to interactive elements</li>
                <li>Use smooth transitions with proper easing</li>
                <li>Test on mobile and desktop</li>
                <li>Document new patterns in DESIGN_SYSTEM.md if novel</li>
            </ol>

            <h3>Performance Guidelines</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Animate only <code>transform</code> and <code>opacity</code> for GPU acceleration</li>
                <li>Avoid animating <code>width</code>, <code>height</code>, <code>left</code>, <code>top</code></li>
                <li>Use <code>will-change</code> sparingly and remove after animation</li>
                <li>Keep animations under 0.5s for page transitions</li>
                <li>Test with DevTools performance monitor</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
